    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/4cff7939ef155540fc52409540c6e388.poster.avif?t=1772282547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/4cff7939ef155540fc52409540c6e388.webm?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/4cff7939ef155540fc52409540c6e388.mp4?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>Residuality is a atmospheric story-rich psychological horror about the spirit world, employ new investigative methods as private investigator Richard as you enter the spirit world to relive the past of the Moriarty family, solve a diverse range of puzzles, overcome horrific entities and solve the mystery surrounding the family and their premise.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/044df7286e3abedf465d5177ff2f4f81.poster.avif?t=1772282547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/044df7286e3abedf465d5177ff2f4f81.webm?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/044df7286e3abedf465d5177ff2f4f81.mp4?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AFTER RECEIVING A PHONE CALL ONE LATE EVENING IN HIS OFFICE PRIVATE DETECTIVE RICHARD EMBARKS ON ONE FINAL CASE TO INVESTIGATE THE DISAPPEARANCE OF THE MORIARTY FAMILY IN THEIR OLD FAMILY ESTATE</strong></h2>Enter the spirit world to relive the past of the Moriarty family and ultimately discover your own truth. As you embark on your final case involving the Moriarty family as private investigator Richard you will face the past and present and be taken into unknown dimensions leading you to places beyond the veil.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/85440af5e36b36c8aef0263340bee47e.poster.avif?t=1772282547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/85440af5e36b36c8aef0263340bee47e.webm?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/85440af5e36b36c8aef0263340bee47e.mp4?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES AND THEMES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Spirit vision - Relive the different experiences from the Moriarty family members perspective<br></li><li>Classical Victorian era, vintage and old cinema themes with hints of lovecraftian horror<br></li><li>Investigation / detective mechanics inspired by Sherlock Holmes<br></li><li>Atmospheric photo realistic locations and realistic audio design<br></li><li>Interactive and diverse atmospheric environments with unique visuals<br></li><li>Reoccurring HUB areas and memory fragments from the veil piece together evidence to progress<br></li><li>Diverse amount of puzzles - stealth mechanics - boss encounters<br></li><li>Original soundtrack and diverse classical tunes and piano melodies<br></li><li>Visual storytelling and a twisted story about Richards demise and the Moriarty families past<br></li><li>Adjustable quality settings available inside the game through ESC &gt; Options.<br></li><li>View, create and manage keybindings of controls inside the game through ESC &gt; Controls.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/101c319e95bdae4b7a96999f853cc7cf.poster.avif?t=1772282547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/101c319e95bdae4b7a96999f853cc7cf.webm?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/101c319e95bdae4b7a96999f853cc7cf.mp4?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/a39f9b4fe25184b7fb9fa93fb8a89844.poster.avif?t=1772282547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/a39f9b4fe25184b7fb9fa93fb8a89844.webm?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810650/extras/a39f9b4fe25184b7fb9fa93fb8a89844.mp4?t=1772282547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2></li></ul>",
